<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { background-color: #f0f0f0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; }
      .wrapper { padding: 40px 20px; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
      .header { background: #F47C20; padding: 28px 20px; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
      .content { padding: 36px 32px; background: #ffffff; }
      .content p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #444444; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      .otp-box { background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px dashed #F47C20; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; padding: 24px 20px; margin: 28px 0; }
      .otp-label { font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: #888888; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .otp-code { font-size: 38px; font-weight: 700; color: #F47C20; letter-spacing: 10px; }
      .otp-expiry { font-size: 12px; color: #999999; margin-top: 10px; }
      .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; margin: 28px 0; }
      .warning { background: #fff8f3; border-left: 4px solid #F47C20; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #666666; margin-bottom: 24px; }
      .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px 32px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa; line-height: 1.6; }
      .footer a { color: #F47C20; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="header">
          <h1>Sendrey</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
          <p>Hey <strong>{{name}}</strong>, welcome back!</p>
          <p>We recognised your account. Use the code below to log in and pick up right where you left off.</p>

          <div class="otp-box">
            <p class="otp-label">Your login code</p>
            <p class="otp-code">{{otp}}</p>
            <p class="otp-expiry">This code expires in <strong>10 minutes</strong></p>
          </div>

          <div class="warning">
            If you did not request this code, someone may have entered your details. You can safely ignore this email — your account remains secure.
          </div>

          <hr class="divider">

          <p>Need help? Reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@sendrey.com" style="color:#F47C20;">support@sendrey.com</a></p>
          <p>— The Sendrey Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>&copy; {{year}} Sendrey. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>